CNN-based Lake Area Forecasting
This repository provides the source code for the CNN-based lake area forecasting workflow used in the associated manuscript. The code includes model training, evaluation, prediction, and an example script for downloading seasonal forecast predictors.

The repository is intentionally lightweight for publication review. It contains the software needed to describe and rerun the workflow, but does not include large raw datasets, processed feature tables, trained model weights, generated figures, or result files.

Repository Structure
.
+-- src/
|   +-- train_cnn.py
|   +-- predict_cnn.py
+-- scripts/
|   +-- download_cds_seasonal.py
