+-- LICENSE
Installation
pip install -r requirements.txt
Training
Run CNN training for one lead time:

python src/train_cnn.py --input data/processed/basin1.csv --leadtime 1 --output results/cnn/leadtime1
For the other lead times, replace basin1.csv and --leadtime 1 with the corresponding files and values.

Prediction
Run prediction with trained CNN weights:

python src/predict_cnn.py --future data/processed/2017.csv --weights results/cnn/leadtime1 --output results/cnn/leadtime1/predictions_leadtime_1.csv
Notes for Reviewers
The public code is a path-independent version of the original local scripts in the CNN workflow. Local machine paths were replaced by command-line arguments so the code can be run in a clean environment.

See DATA_AVAILABILITY.md for the manuscript-ready software and data availability statement.
